{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>Content Warning </i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>This game contains depictions of blood and violence (including vampire bites), depression, and suicide.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u><strong>Velvet Bite:  Softly, With Teeth</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u30d9\u30eb\u30d9\u30c3\u30c8\u00b7\u30d0\u30a4\u30c8 / \u8f7b\u54ac\u4e1d\u7ed2 / \ubca8\ubcb3 \ubc14\uc774\ud2b8</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Romance with Vampires</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You've been invited to a Halloween party! Yay!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Music! Food! Drinks! Vampires!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Wait. VAMPIRES!?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A Romantic Visual Novel</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">featuring 6 romanceable vampires.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u><strong>Main Routes</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Madison</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2894820/extras/Madison.jpg?t=1737580915\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u><i>    That's my question to ask.</i></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u><i>    Why are you here?</i></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Your roommate!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">She's not happy to be around you, obviously.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Forrest</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2894820/extras/Forrest.jpg?t=1737580915\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u><i>    City life isn't good for your mental health.</i></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u><i>    Vampires also need greens to heal.</i></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Kind and caring.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">His dessert wasn't very good. Too bad.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Yvonne</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2894820/extras/Yvonne.jpg?t=1737580915\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u><i>    Hm, what's good for a fairy?</i></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u><i>    Cutie pie? Or sweetheart?</i></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A beauty, known to never age.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Runs a business.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Sebastian</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2894820/extras/Sebastian.jpg?t=1737580915\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u><i>    I mistook you for a different person.</i></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u><i>    I guess I was drunk.</i></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Book lover and movie enthusiast.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Not a social person.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u><strong>Bonus Routes</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Charlotte</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2894820/extras/Charlotte.jpg?t=1737580915\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i><u>    So, was the party worth it?</u></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You